<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="es">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <meta name="theme-color" content="#4f46e5">

    <title>Registro Profesional | Únete a nuestra red de talentos</title>

    <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.4.0/css/all.min.css">
</head>

<body class="bg-gradient-to-br from-indigo-100 via-white to-indigo-200 text-gray-800 font-sans min-h-screen flex items-center justify-center p-4 sm:p-6 relative">

    <main role="main"
        class="w-full max-w-2xl bg-white/80 backdrop-blur-md rounded-xl shadow-xl overflow-hidden border border-white/30">

        <header class="bg-indigo-600 p-6 sm:p-8 text-white">
            <h1 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-bold flex items-center gap-3">
                <i class="fa-solid fa-user-astronaut"></i>
                Registro Profesional
            </h1>
            <p class="text-indigo-100 mt-2 text-sm sm:text-base">
                Completa el siguiente formulario para crear tu perfil.
            </p>
        </header>

        <form class="p-6 sm:p-8 space-y-6">

            <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-6">

                <div>
                    <label class="text-sm font-medium">Nombre</label>
                    <input type="text"
                        class="w-full mt-1 p-2.5 border rounded-lg bg-gray-50 focus:ring-2 focus:ring-indigo-500">
                </div>

                <div>
                    <label class="text-sm font-medium">Correo</label>
                    <input type="email"
                        class="w-full mt-1 p-2.5 border rounded-lg bg-gray-50 focus:ring-2 focus:ring-indigo-500">
                </div>

                <div>
                    <label class="text-sm font-medium">Teléfono</label>
                    <input type="tel"
                        class="w-full mt-1 p-2.5 border rounded-lg bg-gray-50 focus:ring-2 focus:ring-indigo-500">
                </div>

                <div>
                    <label class="text-sm font-medium">Edad</label>
                    <input type="number"
                        class="w-full mt-1 p-2.5 border rounded-lg bg-gray-50 focus:ring-2 focus:ring-indigo-500">
                </div>

                <div class="sm:col-span-2">
                    <label class="text-sm font-medium">Especialidad</label>
                    <select
                        class="w-full mt-1 p-2.5 border rounded-lg bg-gray-50 focus:ring-2 focus:ring-indigo-500">
                        <option>Frontend</option>
                        <option>Backend</option>
                        <option>Fullstack</option>
                    </select>
                </div>

                <div class="sm:col-span-2">
                    <label class="text-sm font-medium">Biografía</label>
                    <textarea rows="4"
                        class="w-full mt-1 p-2.5 border rounded-lg bg-gray-50 focus:ring-2 focus:ring-indigo-500"></textarea>
                </div>

            </div>

            <button
                class="w-full bg-indigo-600 hover:bg-indigo-700 text-white py-3 rounded-lg font-semibold transition">
                Enviar Registro
            </button>

        </form>

    </main>

</body>

</html>
